Package bss.Keywords

Enum Categories

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<Categories>
bss.Keywords.Categories
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<Categories>, java.lang.constant.Constable
public enum Categories extends Enum<Categories>
Enum representing various categories and terms related to products. Acts as a dictionary for storing and managing terms and synonyms applicable to different product attributes.
